Installing the TypeCast.

 * You have already got codes from svn, you look this document.

    % svn co http://typecastmobile.googlecode.com/svn/trunk tc

 * Installing CPAN modules used by TypeCast.

    % cd tc
    % perl -Ilib -MCPAN -e 'install Bundle::TypeCast'

 * Create configuration file and editting some settings for your environment.

    % cp mt-config.cgi-original mt-config.cgi


Installing MovableType Plugin if you need.

  This plugin extends the Movable Type Atom API for TypeCast.
  This plugin requires MTOS 4.15 beta4 or greator.

 * Move the mtplugin/TypeCast directory to your plugins directory.
